rows.label: qst003401_msg0002
rows.name: You buy what we make for dirt cheap!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0003
rows.name:
But you rip us off for
Superbia's industrial goods!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0004
rows.name:
On top of that, an accident at
your base broke the water tower,
and you lot won't even fix it!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0005
rows.name:
Vegetables need water to grow!
Don't you even know that much?!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0101
rows.name:
We Superbian soldiers are
not responsible for
destroying the water tower!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0103
rows.name:
...those Drivers over there! If you
have a complaint, tell it to them!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0104
rows.name:
What...? So you're the
ones who broke it!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0105
rows.name:
Do you have any idea how much
trouble we've had watering the
fields since it broke?!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0106
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Hah! Perfect! We'll take out
our frustration on you!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0202
rows.name: My apologies for this unseemly display!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0203
rows.name:
Huh? Unseemly? We came here to
have a serious discussion!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0204
rows.name: Hey, you. Are you this guy's superior?

rows.label: qst003401_msg0205
rows.name:
I bet you won't listen
to reason either!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0206
rows.name:
Fine! We'll show you
just how angry we are!
